Uh...

00:08.943 --> 00:11.944
FRANCINE (seductive voice):
My name is Staniella.

00:11.946 --> 00:15.280
Okay.

00:15.282 --> 00:17.516
(normal voice)
<i> Where can I hide the bug?</i>

00:17.518 --> 00:19.718
<i> In the dresser?</i>
<i> No, this is a motel.</i>

00:19.720 --> 00:22.888
<i>  He'll leave right after we</i>
<i>have  full-on rubber-less sex.</i>

00:22.890 --> 00:24.623
<i> Got it.</i>

00:29.063 --> 00:31.230
(coughs) Did I just swallow one
of your teeth?

00:31.232 --> 00:33.399
FRANCINE:
Why am I recording all this?

00:33.401 --> 00:35.401
STAN:
'Cause I'm supposed to be

00:35.403 --> 00:37.236
a woman on this mission.
You're a spy?

00:37.238 --> 00:40.072
