for taking you to Jared's.

00:40.074 --> 00:41.206
(whack!)

00:44.645 --> 00:46.578
She disappeared.

00:46.580 --> 00:48.080
Like ghost.

00:48.082 --> 00:51.450
Another perfect
American spy operation.

